org.framed.orm.ui.action

Class RolesDialog

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.jface.window.Window
      • org.eclipse.jface.dialogs.Dialog
        • org.framed.orm.ui.action.RolesDialog
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.eclipse.jface.window.IShellProvider

    public class RolesDialog
extends org.eclipse.jface.dialogs.Dialog
    A dialog class for creating a dialog, which let the user choose the Shapes from type roletype and rolegroup he wants to add or to remove from a Relation from type fulfillment. With this the user decides, which RoleTypes and RoleGroups the source of the Fulfillment fulfills.
    Author:
    Kay Bierzynski (initial development), Lars Schuetze (use EMF adapters)
